Ex-Citigroup Executive Foster Pleads Guilty to Bank Fraud

-- B y   T h o m   W e i d l i c h
-- 
2011-09-06T15:59:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-06/ex-citigroup-executive-foster-pleads-guilty-to-22-million-embezzlement.html
Gary Foster, a former  Citigroup Inc. (C) 
vice president accused of embezzling $22.9 million from the
bank, pleaded guilty to one count of bank fraud in federal court
in  Brooklyn ,  New York .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Thom Weidlich in New York at 
